-- Twitter Says Issues Accessing Site Have Been Resolved
-- B y   B r i a n   W o m a c k
-- 2012-06-21T17:44:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-21/twitter-says-users-may-be-experiencing-issues-accessing-site.html
Twitter Inc. said its microblogging
service is “currently operational” after some users earlier
today had difficulty accessing the website.  “The issue has been resolved,” the company said on a
blog. Carolyn Penner, a spokeswoman for San Francisco-based
Twitter, confirmed in an e-mailed statement that the site is
operational.  To contact the reporter on this story:
